5wxu2rody7o.png\" title=\"Email Sequence\" alt=\"Email Sequence\" loading=\"lazy\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"elementor-image-box-content\"><h3 class=\"elementor-image-box-title\">Email Sequence<\/h3><p class=\"elementor-image-box-description\">RatingE Automation sends review invitation emails on your behalf, ensuring they come directly from your business name.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-097a833 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"097a833\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-25cf5e4 elementor-position-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-box\" data-id=\"25cf5e4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-box-wrapper\"><figure class=\"elementor-image-box-img\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Private-Feedback-qsiech2klvpi9lzsld62nj9hwlkktyozh7l5hdwr5g.png\" title=\"Private Feedback\" alt=\"Private Feedback\" loading=\"lazy\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"elementor-image-box-content\"><h3 class=\"elementor-image-box-title\">Private Feedback<\/h3><p class=\"elementor-image-box-description\">Instead of posting negative reviews, the RatingE System encourages customers to provide private feedback only visible to you.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-19b3626 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"19b3626\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-661a92b elementor-position-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-box\" data-id=\"661a92b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-box-wrapper\"><figure class=\"elementor-image-box-img\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Platform-Integration-qsif7jmiiq8q1kv15so42p00t4fd9s1kezwyknu9h0.png\" title=\"Platform Integration\" alt=\"Platform Integration\" loading=\"lazy\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"elementor-image-box-content\"><h3 class=\"elementor-image-box-title\">Platform Integration<\/h3><p class=\"elementor-image-box-description\">Connect RatingE to platforms like Google, yelp and TripAdvisor to collect and display reviews, all in one system.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5adec04 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5adec04\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d63b49d elementor-position-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-box\" data-id=\"d63b49d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-box-wrapper\"><figure class=\"elementor-image-box-img\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/ratinge.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Website-Display-qsifgyy91x58gt654dcfktdf97yvgigo1nf8tjv52s.png\" title=\"Website Display\" alt=\"Website Display\" loading=\"lazy\" \/><\/figure><div class=\"elementor-image-box-content\"><h3 class=\"elementor-image-box-title\">Website Display<\/h3><p class=\"elementor-image-box-description\">Easily showcase positive text reviews on your website by copying and pasting the HTML code from the RatingE System.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f1a21af e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f1a21af\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e19241 elementor-position-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-box\" data-id=\"2e19241\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-box-wrapper\"><figure class=\"elementor-image-box-img\"><img decoding=\"